INSERT INTO table_snapshot(warehouse_id,
                                      table_id,
                                      snapshot_id,
                                      parent_snapshot_id,
                                      sequence_number,
                                      manifest_list,
                                      summary,
                                      schema_id,
                                      timestamp_ms,
                                      first_row_id,
                                      assigned_rows,
                                      key_id)
            SELECT $3, $2, * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::BIGINT[],
                $4::BIGINT[],
                $5::BIGINT[],
                $6::TEXT[],
                $7::JSONB[],
                $8::INT[],
                $9::BIGINT[],
                $10::BIGINT[],
                $11::BIGINT[],
                $12::TEXT[]
            )
